billing_emails_modal.billing_emails_info.string: True-ups let you confirm the number of full seats you're paying for on your next invoice.
True-ups are emailed every 3 months from your subscription start date. Reminders are also sent 28 days before, 2 weeks before, and 3 days before each true-up. {more}
We keep all admins and billing contacts informed about renewals, invoices, and more.
This annual subscription renews on {date} and renews every year on that date. Figma sends reminders 14 days and 5 days before a renewal to all admins.
What billing emails do I get?
